Zinc,is,a,service,that,allows,users,to,purchase,products,from,online,retailers,such,as,Amazon,com,and,ship,the,products,directly,to,their,customers,Zinc,acts,as,a,bridge,between,a,retailer,and,applications,The,Zinc,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Zinc,with,other,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,placing,orders,retrieving,orders,and,retrieving,the,status,of,orders